<i>adverb</i>: 하루속히 [하루소키], 하루빨리 [하루빨리], 하루바삐 [하루바삐], 지금 [지금], 즉각 [즉깍], 얼른 [얼른], 썩 [썩], 바로바로 [바로바로], 득달같이 [득딸가치], 냉큼 [냉큼], 금세 [금세], 금방 [금방], 곧바로 [곧빠로], 곧 [곧] <i>noun</i>: 즉시 [즉씨], 단박 [단박] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>하루속히 [하루소키]</dt><br>
<dd>as soon as possible; immediately; quickly</dd><br>
<dd>하루라도 빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>As soon as possible.</dd><br>
<dt>하루빨리 [하루빨리]</dt><br>
<dd>as soon as possible; immediately; quickly</dd><br>
<dd>하루라도 빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>As soon as possible.</dd><br>
<dt>하루바삐 [하루바삐]</dt><br>
<dd>as soon as possible; immediately; quickly</dd><br>
<dd>하루라도 빨리.</dd><br>
<dd>As soon as possible.</dd><br>
<dt>지금 [지금]</dt><br>
<dd>1. now; immediately</dd><br>
<dd>말을 하고 있는 바로 이때에. 또는 그 즉시에.</dd><br>
<dd>At the present moment as one speaks, or that instant.</dd><br>
<dd>2. now; at this moment</dd><br>
<dd>과거나 미래가 아닌 현재에.</dd><br>
<dd>At present rather than in the past or future.</dd><br>
<dt>즉각 [즉깍]</dt><br>
<dd>immediately</dd><br>
<dd>바로 당장.</dd><br>
<dd>Right away</dd><br>
<dt>얼른 [얼른]</dt><br>
<dd>quickly; immediately; promptly</dd><br>
<dd>시간을 오래 끌지 않고 바로.</dd><br>
<dd>Right away without lingering over something.</dd><br>
<dt>썩 [썩]</dt><br>
<dd>1. exceedingly; greatly; so</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 들 정도로 아주.</dd><br>
<dd>Very much, enough to please one.</dd><br>
<dd>2. right away; immediately</dd><br>
<dd>지금 바로.</dd><br>
<dd>Right now.</dd><br>
<dt>바로바로 [바로바로]</dt><br>
<dd>immediately</dd><br>
<dd>그때그때 곧.</dd><br>
<dd>Right away, at this moment.</dd><br>
<dt>득달같이 [득딸가치]</dt><br>
<dd>immediately</dd><br>
<dd>잠시도 늦추지 않고 아주 빠르게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very quickly without slowing down even for a moment.</dd><br>
<dt>냉큼 [냉큼]</dt><br>
<dd>immediately; promptly</dd><br>
<dd>머뭇거리지 않고 빨리.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly without hesitation.</dd><br>
<dt>금세 [금세]</dt><br>
<dd>immediately; soon</dd><br>
<dd>시간이 얼마 지나지 않아서.</dd><br>
<dd>Before long; shortly</dd><br>
<dt>금방 [금방]</dt><br>
<dd>1. moment ago</dd><br>
<dd>바로 얼마 전에.</dd><br>
<dd>A short time ago.</dd><br>
<dd>2. at any moment</dd><br>
<dd>지금이라도 당장.</dd><br>
<dd>At any minute now.</dd><br>
<dd>3. immediately; soon</dd><br>
<dd>시간이 얼마 지나지 않아 곧바로.</dd><br>
<dd>Before long; shortly</dd><br>
<dd>4. quickly</dd><br>
<dd>걸리는 시간이 짧게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of taking a short time.</dd><br>
<dt>곧바로 [곧빠로]</dt><br>
<dd>1. immediately</dd><br>
<dd>바로 즉시에.</dd><br>
<dd>Instantly</dd><br>
<dd>2. straight up; upright</dd><br>
<dd>곧은 방향으로.</dd><br>
<dd>In a straight line.</dd><br>
<dd>3. straight; directly</dd><br>
<dd>다른 곳을 거치거나 들르지 않고 바로.</dd><br>
<dd>Immediately without stopping by other places.</dd><br>
<dd>4. at a short distance; close by</dd><br>
<dd>멀지 않고 바로 가까이에.</dd><br>
<dd>Near, not far away.</dd><br>
<dt>곧 [곧]</dt><br>
<dd>1. immediately</dd><br>
<dd>지체하지 않고 바로.</dd><br>
<dd>Quickly without delay.</dd><br>
<dd>2. soon; shortly</dd><br>
<dd>시간이 많이 흐르지 않고 머지않아.</dd><br>
<dd>Before long.</dd><br>
<dd>3. in other words; namely</dd><br>
<dd>바꾸어 말하면.</dd><br>
<dd>That is to say; put differently.</dd><br>
<dd>4. none other than</dd><br>
<dd>바로 다름 아닌.</dd><br>
<dd>Nothing less than.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>즉시 [즉씨]</dt><br>
<dd>immediately</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이 벌어진 바로 그때.</dd><br>
<dd>At the very time when something is happening.</dd><br>
<dt>단박 [단박]</dt><br>
<dd>at once; immediately; on the spot; right away</dd><br>
<dd>그 자리에서 바로.</dd><br>
<dd>Done immediately right on the spot.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>